 ('3', '56', 'en_us', 'Leaders in design of surface transportation systems for nearly three decades ', 'Transportation Engineering ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-26 21:28:58', '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '1b514ff4-d8b9-47ab-9813-1471d468b61d'),
 ('6', '93', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Our team of highway, bridge, traffic engineers, and planners collaborate on a wide range of transportation system improvement projects.', '<p>In the public sector, we assist state agencies and municipalities in improving and expanding existing infrastructure. In the private sector, we assist clients in building infrastructure in support of residential, commercial, and other opportunities for growth. While performing a wide range of services, commonalities in design include multi-modal considerations, safe mobility, public consensus, and minimizing impacts to the environment.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '831c3e7c-e8df-4b5d-9bbb-b80d7d0cc03c'),
 ('7', '114', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'left', 'We pride ourselves on an environmental and community based approach to design. ', '<p>Our highway, bridge, and traffic engineers routinely collaborate with our planners, landscape architects, and environmental scientists for repeated success on projects. Our goal on every project is to enhance mobility for all travel modes without compromising safety or adversely impacting the environment.  Whether widening a highway, enhancing operations along a signalized corridor, or rehabilitating a historic bridge, we achieve success by engaging project stakeholders and partners with regulatory agencies, ensuring compatibility between transportation facilities and the surrounding environment and communities we work in.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '5b991018-62f5-4cca-9ec6-545b17d695f7'),
 ('8', '115', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Our Transporation & Traffic Team ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '2017-06-28 13:35:02', '63466302-2319-4845-8b66-9870e27e1737'),
 ('9', '116', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, 'See how we\'ve improved transportation and traffic flow ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:35:03', '2017-06-28 13:35:03', 'f8d2dd47-30e7-49b9-b2fc-b4b76cfe3c7c'),
 ('10', '132', 'en_us', 'Transforming communities to meet changing needs ', 'Planning', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:56:24', '2017-06-28 14:52:19', '916e8729-6af2-4444-9233-2daebe7ac33e'),
 ('11', '134', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Planning is not a linear, rigid process but rather evolves during the planning period. ', '<p>Planning is the framework from which present and future challenges are addressed in a thoughtful, stakeholder-driven process, and the complexity of these challenges requires a range of professional training and experience. At Milone &amp; MacBroom, each assignment is guided by senior planning staff that have direct access to the resources of our entire organization.<br /></p>\n<p>As “what ifs” and “whys” emerge, our staff provides creative solutions based on sound analysis using GIS, mapping, public outreach, and traditional and new media approaches. Our team members pride themselves on their ability to work effectively with public and private sector stakeholders, as well as the general public, to achieve the desired outcome for every project on which they work.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:56:24', '2017-06-28 14:52:19', 'eded90e6-0806-4268-91d2-f6cd932d0766'),
 ('12', '135', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Our specific planning services include: ', NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:56:24', '2017-06-28 14:52:19', '297cfcbe-0857-4cdb-9283-8617d746df2d'),
 ('13', '136', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 13:56:24', '2017-06-28 14:52:19', '2d161604-3b59-41f8-81f8-4329e40264da'),
