 ('22', '148', 'en_us', 'Transforming communities through the fusion of art and science.  ', 'About Milone & MacBroom', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 19:29:30', '2017-06-28 19:29:30', '6fa3dc66-ec3e-49a5-ad7d-c990b542fa03'),
 ('23', '150', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'We solve problems with highly-efficient, sustainable solutions, adaptive designs, and technical precision. ', '<p>Milone &amp; MacBroom is one of the largest consulting firms in the northeast, offering a diverse set of specialty practices in the fields of engineering, planning, landscape architecture, and environmental science. We serve a multitude of industries from Government and NGO to Cities and Municipalities. Unlink niche companies or enterprise firms, Milone &amp; MacBroom has local expertise, cross functional teams, and a relationship first approach that sets us apart. That, combined with our technical precision, attention to detail, and passion behind our work, helps us to deliver the most efficient and sustainable solutions offered. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-06-28 19:29:30', '2017-06-28 19:29:30', '76f7a04a-bd35-410f-9627-621c480a8be1'),
